<h2 id="speaker-bio">Speaker bio</h2>

<p>Erik Jhordan Rey is a Software Engineer passionate to build technology products. He worked on a variety of software projects. He loves to share experiences, and lessons learned about design software systems, patterns, and practices that make it easier to build useful software. He also enjoys managing, leading, and building engineering teams to help companies produce highly desirable and quality products that drive business impact.</p>

